---
import PageLayout from "@/layouts/Base.astro";

const meta = {
	description: "Learn more about me, my journey as a developer, and what drives my passion for creating amazing web experiences.",
	title: "About Me",
};
---

<PageLayout meta={meta}>
	<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
		<h1 class="title mb-8 text-center">About Me</h1>
		
		<div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-12 mb-12">
			<!-- Profile Image and Quick Info -->
			<div class="lg:col-span-1">
				<div class="text-center mb-8">
					<img 
						src="/avatar.jpg" 
						alt="Your Name" 
						class="w-48 h-48 rounded-2xl mx-auto mb-6 border-4 border-accent-one/20 shadow-lg"
					/>
					<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-2 bg-gradient-to-r from-accent-two to-accent-one bg-clip-text text-transparent">
						Your Name
					</h2>
					<p class="text-accent mb-4">Full-Stack Developer</p>
					<div class="flex flex-col space-y-2 text-sm">
						<span class="flex items-center justify-center">
							<svg class="w-4 h-4 mr-2 text-accent-one" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
								<path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M5.05 4.05a7 7 0 119.9 9.9L10 18.9l-4.95-4.95a7 7 0 010-9.9zM10 11a2 2 0 100-4 2 2 0 000 4z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
							</svg>
							San Francisco, CA
						</span>
						<span class="flex items-center justify-center">
							<svg class="w-4 h-4 mr-2 text-accent-one" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
								<path d="M2.003 5.884L10 9.882l7.997-3.998A2 2 0 0016 4H4a2 2 0 00-1.997 1.884z" />
								<path d="M18 8.118l-8 4-8-4V14a2 2 0 002 2h12a2 2 0 002-2V8.118z" />
							</svg>
							your.email@domain.com
						</span>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>

			<!-- Main Content -->
			<div class="lg:col-span-2">
				<div class="prose prose-citrus max-w-none">
					<h2 class="text-accent-two mb-4">My Story</h2>
					<p class="mb-6 leading-relaxed">
						Hello! I'm a passionate full-stack developer with over 5 years of experience creating 
						digital experiences that matter. My journey into programming started during college when 
						I built my first website for a local business – seeing how technology could solve real 
						problems sparked a passion that continues to drive me today.
					</p>

					<p class="mb-6 leading-relaxed">
						I specialize in modern web technologies like React, Node.js, and TypeScript, but I'm 
						always exploring new tools and frameworks. What excites me most is the intersection of 
						great design and robust functionality – creating applications that are not only powerful 
						but also delightful to use.
					</p>

					<h2 class="text-accent-two mb-4">What I Do</h2>
					<p class="mb-6 leading-relaxed">
						Currently, I work as a Senior Frontend Developer at TechCorp, where I lead a team of 
						developers building scalable web applications. I'm also a freelance consultant, helping 
						startups and small businesses bring their digital visions to life.
					</p>

					<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-8">
						<div class="bg-special-light p-6 rounded-lg border border-color-200">
							<h3 class="text-accent font-semibold mb-3">Frontend Development</h3>
							<p class="text-sm text-textColor leading-relaxed">
								Building responsive, accessible, and performant user interfaces with modern 
								frameworks and best practices.
							</p>
						</div>
						<div class="bg-special-light p-6 rounded-lg border border-color-200">
							<h3 class="text-accent font-semibold mb-3">Backend Development</h3>
							<p class="text-sm text-textColor leading-relaxed">
								Designing robust APIs and server architectures that scale with your business needs.
							</p>
						</div>
						<div class="bg-special-light p-6 rounded-lg border border-color-200">
							<h3 class="text-accent font-semibold mb-3">UI/UX Design</h3>
							<p class="text-sm text-textColor leading-relaxed">
								Creating intuitive user experiences through thoughtful design and user research.
							</p>
						</div>
						<div class="bg-special-light p-6 rounded-lg border border-color-200">
							<h3 class="text-accent font-semibold mb-3">Consulting</h3>
							<p class="text-sm text-textColor leading-relaxed">
								Helping teams adopt new technologies and improve their development processes.
							</p>
						</div>
					</div>

					<h2 class="text-accent-two mb-4">Beyond Code</h2>
					<p class="mb-6 leading-relaxed">
						When I'm not coding, you'll find me hiking in the mountains, experimenting with new 
						recipes in the kitchen, or contributing to open-source projects. I'm also passionate 
						about mentoring aspiring developers and regularly speak at local meetups and conferences.
					</p>

					<p class="mb-8 leading-relaxed">
						I believe in continuous learning and staying curious. Whether it's exploring a new 
						programming language, diving into machine learning, or understanding the latest design 
						trends, I'm always looking for ways to grow and improve my craft.
					</p>

					<div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-accent-one/10 to-accent-two/10 p-6 rounded-lg border border-accent-one/20">
						<h3 class="text-accent font-semibold mb-3">Let's Connect!</h3>
						<p class="text-textColor mb-4 leading-relaxed">
							I'm always interested in new opportunities and collaborations. Whether you want to 
							discuss a project, share ideas, or just chat about technology, feel free to reach out!
						</p>
						<div class="flex space-x-4 flex-wrap gap-2">
							<a href="/contact/" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center h-10 px-4 rounded-lg bg-gradient-to-r from-accent-one to-accent-two text-bgColor font-medium hover:brightness-110 transition-all">
								Get In Touch
							</a>
							<a href="/resume.pdf" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center h-10 px-4 rounded-lg border-2 border-accent-one/30 hover:border-accent-one/50 text-accent font-medium transition-all">
								Download Resume
							</a>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>

		<!-- Timeline/Experience Section -->
		<section class="mt-16">
			<h2 class="title mb-8 text-center text-accent-two">Experience</h2>
			<div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
				<div class="relative">
					<!-- Timeline line -->
					<div class="absolute left-4 top-0 bottom-0 w-0.5 bg-accent-one/30"></div>
					
					<!-- Experience items -->
					<div class="space-y-8">
						<div class="relative flex items-start">
							<div class="absolute left-2 w-4 h-4 bg-accent-one rounded-full border-4 border-bgColor"></div>
							<div class="ml-12">
								<div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row sm:items-center sm:justify-between mb-2">
									<h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-accent">Senior Frontend Developer</h3>
									<span class="text-sm text-textColor">2022 - Present</span>
								</div>
								<p class="text-accent-two font-medium mb-2">TechCorp Inc.</p>
								<p class="text-textColor text-sm leading-relaxed">
									Leading frontend development for flagship products, mentoring junior developers, 
									and implementing modern React architectures that improved performance by 40%.
								</p>
							</div>
						</div>

						<div class="relative flex items-start">
							<div class="absolute left-2 w-4 h-4 bg-accent-two rounded-full border-4 border-bgColor"></div>
							<div class="ml-12">
								<div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row sm:items-center sm:justify-between mb-2">
									<h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-accent">Full-Stack Developer</h3>
									<span class="text-sm text-textColor">2020 - 2022</span>
								</div>
								<p class="text-accent-two font-medium mb-2">StartupXYZ</p>
								<p class="text-textColor text-sm leading-relaxed">
									Built and maintained multiple web applications from ground up, working with 
									React, Node.js, and PostgreSQL in a fast-paced startup environment.
								</p>
							</div>
						</div>

						<div class="relative flex items-start">
							<div class="absolute left-2 w-4 h-4 bg-accent-one rounded-full border-4 border-bgColor"></div>
							<div class="ml-12">
								<div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row sm:items-center sm:justify-between mb-2">
									<h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-accent">Junior Developer</h3>
									<span class="text-sm text-textColor">2019 - 2020</span>
								</div>
								<p class="text-accent-two font-medium mb-2">WebAgency Pro</p>
								<p class="text-textColor text-sm leading-relaxed">
									Developed responsive websites and web applications for various clients, 
									gaining experience in modern frontend frameworks and best practices.
								</p>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>
	</div>
</PageLayout>